            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-01-05T21:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-05-31T23:30:00-05:00" n="56" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d56">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Cairo, on September 10, reported information from British Embassy sources that
                    tankers from Venezuela had already arrived at Haifa but that the “Critical
                    tanker” from the Persian Gulf was not due until the end of September (telegram
                    902, 501.BB Palestine/9–2549).</p>
                <p>Cairo advised, on September 27, of further information from British Embassy
                    sources that the coming of the critical tanker had been deferred (telegram 910,
                    867N.6363/9–2749).</p>
            </div>
